<% content_for :heading do -%>
  Find A Trend
<% end -%>

This website allows you to map currency values to popular news stories from that time period, with the goal of providing understanding as to why the market moves the way it does.<br /><br />

<center>
<% form_for :currency, :url => {:action => :show}, :html => {:method => :get} do |f| %>
  <%= f.collection_select :currency_name, Currency.all, :name, :description, {}, :class => 'dropdown' %>
  <br /><br />
  <%= f.submit 'Tell Me Why?', :class => 'button' %>
<% end -%>
</center>
